summary: NEW COMIC DAY TODAY, OUR PICKS: LIFE OF CAPTAIN MARVEL #1 -- We’ve been long-time fans of CAPTAIN MARVEL and Carol Danvers, and...
caption:
NEW COMIC DAY TODAY, OUR PICKS: LIFE OF CAPTAIN MARVEL #1 – We’ve been long-time fans of CAPTAIN MARVEL and Carol Danvers, and when we saw she’d be one of the next Marvel icons to make her way to the silver screen courtesy of the Marvel Cinematic Universe — we were pretty stoked!
Now, Marvel is giving you a perfect chance to learn all about who Captain Marvel is, and what she’s all about in this new limited series chronicling her origins, and where she is now in the Marvel U today!
Carol Danvers was just a girl from the Boston suburbs who loved science and the Red Sox until a chance encounter with a Kree hero gave her incredible super-powers.
Now, she’s a leader in the Avengers and the commander of Alpha Flight. But what if there were more to the story?
When crippling anxiety attacks put her on the sidelines in the middle of a fight, Carol finds herself reliving memories of a life she thought was far behind her.
You can’t outrun where you’re from – and sometimes, you HAVE to go home again. But there are skeletons in Captain Marvel’s closet – and what she discovers will change her entire world.
Written by best-selling author Margaret Stohl and drawn by fan-favorite comics veteran Carlos Pacheco, this is the true origin of Captain Marvel.
